<i>Hentikan saya, hentikan saya, hentikan saya</i>

874
01:00:26,748 --> 01:00:27,957
Dia orang gila.

875
01:00:38,593 --> 01:00:40,595
Peguam Shin, awak okay?

876
01:00:53,107 --> 01:00:56,402
Ya.

877
01:00:57,737 --> 01:01:00,698
Ia mungkin kerana saya tidak dapat
banyak tidur sejak beberapa hari lalu.

878
01:01:01,324 --> 01:01:03,701
Awak kelihatan pucat.
Saya rasa awak patut berehat.

879
01:01:05,703 --> 01:01:07,455
Okay. Saya akan pulang
selepas menyusun beberapa kertas sedikit.

880
01:01:09,374 --> 01:01:10,375
Saya tidak apa-apa. Pulang tanpa saya.

881
01:01:11,167 --> 01:01:14,212
- Jangan tinggal terlalu lewat.
- Okay.

882
01:01:21,678 --> 01:01:23,179
BANGUNAN OKCHEON

883
01:01:23,262 --> 01:01:27,350
{\an8}PEGUAM SHIN I-RANG

884
01:01:27,433 --> 01:01:30,895
Sekali lagi?

885
01:01:30,978 --> 01:01:32,980
{\an8}Hantu tak datang?

886
01:01:33,064 --> 01:01:34,774
{\an8}<i>Dia sedang membersihkan</i>
<i>untuk pelanggan masa depannya yang masih hidup.</i>

887
01:01:34,857 --> 01:01:38,569
{\an8}Dia sangat teruja.

888
01:01:38,653 --> 01:01:39,696
{\an8}Hooray untuk kemerdekaan I-rang!

889
01:01:39,779 --> 01:01:41,823
{\an8}- Inginkan kes?
<i>- Anda yang terbaik.</i>

890
01:01:54,127 --> 01:01:56,129
{\an8}Saya sangat berpengalaman
dalam kes jualan pra-pembinaan.

891
01:02:17,108 --> 01:02:19,527
{\an8}<i>Peguam Han?</i>

892
01:02:20,027 --> 01:02:21,279
{\an8}<i>- Kenapa awak ada di sini?</i>
<i>- Ini bukan urusan anda.</i>

893
01:02:21,821 --> 01:02:24,449
{\an8}Ada apa dengan kamu?

894
01:02:24,532 --> 01:02:27,243
{\an8}<i>Ia Seongmyeong Construction,</i>

895
01:02:27,910 --> 01:02:30,705
{\an8}<i>sebuah syarikat teduh yang menjalankan</i>
<i>skim penipuan pra-jualan.</i>

896
01:02:31,247 --> 01:02:33,875
{\an8}- Satu kumpulan pembinaan?
- Awak pandai bergaduh, kan?

897
01:02:34,542 --> 01:02:36,586
{\an8}Kamu punk!

898
01:02:47,180 --> 01:02:50,683
{\an8}Terjemahan sari kata oleh: Eunjin Erica Kim [[n]]

899
01:02:57,440 --> 01:03:00,109
{\an8}ATTORNEY SHIN I-RANG

900
01:03:32,850 --> 01:03:33,851
Again?

901
01:04:21,941 --> 01:04:22,775
{\an8}Ghosts aren't coming?

902
01:04:22,859 --> 01:04:24,777
{\an8}<i>He's cleaning</i>
<i>for his future living clients.</i>

903
01:04:24,861 --> 01:04:26,028
{\an8}He's so excited.

904
01:04:26,112 --> 01:04:28,281
{\an8}Hooray for I-rang's independence!

905
01:04:28,364 --> 01:04:29,866
{\an8}- Want a case?
<i>- You're the best.</i>

906
01:04:29,949 --> 01:04:32,785
{\an8}I'm very experienced
in pre-construction sales cases.

907
01:04:33,286 --> 01:04:34,453
{\an8}<i>Attorney Han?</i>

908
01:04:34,537 --> 01:04:36,205
{\an8}<i>- Why are you here?</i>
<i>- It's not your business.</i>

909
01:04:36,289 --> 01:04:37,290
{\an8}What's with you people?

910
01:04:37,373 --> 01:04:38,541
{\an8}<i>It's Seongmyeong Construction,</i>

911
01:04:38,624 --> 01:04:40,668
{\an8}<i>a shady company that runs</i>
<i>a pre-sale fraud scheme.</i>

912
01:04:40,751 --> 01:04:43,004
{\an8}- A construction gang?
- You're good at fighting, right?

913
01:04:43,087 --> 01:04:44,797
{\an8}You little punks!

914
01:04:45,840 --> 01:04:50,845
{\an8}Subtitle translation by: Eunjin Erica Kim

